Mother Deen constantly asks about it, but everyone gives her a different answer. Mother Deen is convinced she is dead. The mental state of Mother Deen is deteriorating. 1.title: Welkom op Vlieland
1.plot: Maria wants to protect her daughter for the danger of her pregnancy, but Wendy has other plans. Sven returned to the island again, after he suddenly disappears three months ago. Femke gets an unexpected exciting visit. Oscar moved in by Maria and he has his sights on a new project, but Maria is less more enthusiastic . Robbert has something to celebrate and organize a party on the beach. His friend Paul comes for the first time after his accident back on the island. Isa is working hard on her career, as a accomplished movie star enters she the red carpet.

2.title: Een riskant plan
2.plot: Robbert wants to help his best friend Paul and has made a risky plan. Fedde wants to cooperate with his plan, but Maria is totally against and unintentional she ensures Robbert become in even more danger. Wendy is very happy with her newborn daughter, unfortunately she is confronted by consequences of teenage motherhood. A great love of Oscar comes to Vlieland. Oscar asks her if she stays to work with him to run the beach club. Femke finds out about a hidden family secret.

3.title: Yuri
3.plot: Jan Barendtz wakes up on the dike and can't remember anything from the night before. Femke hasn't come come all night and Maria is deeply worried. Vlieland gets a mysterious new inhabitant, who will report at Maria's practice. Robbert takes Paul on a night out, to cheer him up. The night goes well for Paul, but the night ends not as planned. Oscar makes an extraordinary discovery as he enters his own house.

4.title: Je kunt niet alles krijgen wat je wilt
4.plot: Robbert finds a weird spot on the leg of Eva and he is sending her to Maria. Eva turns out to be sicker then everyone expected. Femke suffers from her forgetfulness, and she decides to make bucket list together with Hans. Robbert makes several attempts to obtain illegal medications. Maria wants Wendy goes further with her study, but Wendy wants stay at home and take care for her daughter. This makes for a conflict between them with far-reaching consequences. And who exactly is the new pastor where everyone is talking about? Isa goes to investigate.

5.title: Alleen
5.plot: The lawsuit from Wendy expires different than she expected, but will this changes about her decision? Oscar and Maria are fighting. Does this mean the end of their relationship? Heleen wants that Joey come to home again. Isa misses Fedde very much and takes a drastic decision. Femke goes along with Hans to Apeldoorn. The horses in the stables appear to have an infectious disease, can Maria save the horses and her own?

6.title: Verrassing
6.plot: Maria goes to a psychiatrist and discovers more about herself and her past than she had expected. Wendy does everything to get the custody of her child and involves a lie for its own sake. Isa surprises Fedde and Maria with a decision that she has taken. Eva's biological clock is starting to tick, and Robbert is not ready to think about children. Paul is starting to get sick by Robbert's treatment. Maria does a very surprising discovery with the help of Isa.

7.title: Geloof, hoop en liefde
7.plot: Maria gets a surprise visit from her Oscar during the night, which make him deep in trouble. Maria wonders why all men in heat life run away from her during the session by the psychiatrist. After this visit is Maria going to visit for the first time the house of Sven. Paul gets nasty side effects of the treatment from Robbert and got into serious difficulties. Isa thinks the new pastor is gay, but will be disappointed. And is it the end for good for Oscar and Maria?

8.title: Liefde in de Lucht
8.plot: Maria's psychiatrist Max comes to Vlieland, other residents wonder if he really is just for her therapy or just for her. Little Femke is sick and Wendy is very worried, but she won't go for help to her mother. Maria's appointment with Max is making Oscar suspicious. Oscar now lives with Robbert and Eva and is forced to sleep on the couch. He wants his house back, but Eva is just not ready to leave. Eva has a little surprise with major implications for Robbert. Forgetful Femke had to save her beloved by not forgetting him.

9.title: Een besmettelijke ziekte
9.plot: Jan Barendtz does a dangerous discovery on the beach, which has a major impact on the island. The entire population of Vlieland will be quarantined. The psychiatrist of Maria has a problem with their cooperation. Maria understands nothing of it at all. Will he also leave her? Femke doesn't want to stroke a tiger, because she does not know whether she has chosen to do this for her bucket list. Femke thinks Hans can get a much better woman because she is so forgetful. Robbert and Eva go through a deep valley in their relationship. Isa and the reverend face major ...

1.title: Lust
1.plot: The rest on the island is restored after the great wedding of Freek and Isa. It is Wendy and Paul hard to live with their baby in the small house of mother Deen. The forgetfulness of Femke is getting worse by the day. Her friend Hans Hazelbag is the victim of it. Oscars daughter Eva will take a final decision, since it is over with Jelle. Maria gets at the funeral of her father a shocking message. She seeks solace from her ex-psychiatrist Max, so they miss her appointment with Oscar.

2.title: Jaloezie
2.plot: Max makes for a surprise. Oscar is not as charmed. Maria is embarrassed and takes a rigorous decision. Wendy has to make choices, is she studying or will she stays home to care for her family? Robbert has a bright idea to get an internship. He does everything to achieve his goal. Gerda had to deal with a difficult choice. How will Maria respond? Isa hears that her grandfather was not her grandfather.

3.title: Verlies
3.plot: Mother Deen and Paul make a nice vehicle for Paul. Joey goes swimming in the sea, but Mother Deen finds it much too cold for that. Isa goes in search of her roots. She takes Freek with her in the hope that he can open doors for her.

4.title: Verdriet
4.plot: Klaartje replaces Gerda in practice, until they find a new assistant for Maria. Then Klaartje making a big mistake. Robbert do not know who ended up in his bed, he don't know the name of the girl anymore. The wife of policeman De Beer wants to end her life. Maria wants to help her , but decided in collision with De Beer. Heleen can't sleep, she can not even cry. Isa has struggled to find answers to her questions and Wendy makes a discovery. Sven tries to help Oscar, they meditate together.

5.title: Verwarring
5.plot: Maria gets a letter from the medical disciplinary tribunal and enlists the help of Oscar. Oscar is now living in a special place on the island. Priest Bart Vos visits Maria and her family and makes an unexpected announcement. Isa babysit small Femke and start experiencing rattling ovaries. That causes problems between Isa and Freek. Robbert is harassed by a girl he met . His mother is not happy. De Beer avenges the death of his wife on Wendy and Paul, but the Vlielanders help Wendy and Paul.

6.title: Schuldgevoel
6.plot: Maria must come. Oscar defends her ardently , but there's a dead body in the closet. The smart but very young Pip is the observer of Maria. She makes a great impression on Robbert. He also learns the consequences of his actions. Isa and Freek have problems while Wendy loose going in Leeuwarden. Maria congratulates Oscar for his role as a lawyer.

7.title: Liefde
7.plot: Maria is afraid of the judgment of the medical disciplinary tribunal. Oscar already preparing an appeal for. Wendy thinks of cohabitation with Stefan, but keeps her life on Vlieland secret for her friends. Isa fights for her great love Freek. Mother Dees sees Bart Vos for another. Heleen accept the death of her child. Together with her friends, she tries to say goodbye. Pip says the same against Robbert as Maria tells Oscar. Both Robbert and Oscar are surprised.

8.title: Verrassing
8.plot: It seems again amiss between Maria and Oscar. However, their relationship is put under pressure again as Robbert gets a visit from an old friend. Heleen's life is completely turned upside down again when message came from the police from Berlin. Gerda does a nasty discovery that it makes you think. Wendy says she needs to work on Vlieland and go home. But Wendy and Paul get very unexpected visit. Paul and Isa seek solace together as their lives take a nasty turn.

9.title: Angst
9.plot: Heleen is panicking and asking Maria for help. Maria discovers that Joey slightly and has on his liver. Isa picks no longer that Wendy is gone and goes to get her. Wendy is torn between her two lives, she have to make choices. Pip has thought and Robbert gets her on the boat. Then he makes something that will change his life for good. Mary saves a life, almost to the detriment of herself. Mother Deen has a solution for baby Femke.

10.title: Vreugde
10.plot: Wendy misses Femke and requires Stefan openness and honesty about their relationship. Joey turns negative just positive. He should tell something to Heleen. Sven comes to Vlieland for the birthday of Maria. Oscar wants to buy rings, but Maria won't. With the arrival of Finn, Eva wants to start a family with Robbert. Robbert don't want to lose Pip. Maria says "Daddy" to Bart . Femke is very satisfied with it. The family surprised Maria for her sixtieth birthday , but she herself creates the biggest surprise .

imdb.plot outline: Dokter Deen lives on the Dutch isle of Vlieland where she has a docter's practice and deals with every day life in a small town community. She deals with issues with her ex-husband and her new lover, her children and her mother who suffers from dementia.
imdb.title: Dokter Deen
plot: Doctor Maria Deen lives with her mother Femke and her three children on a island. She helps the people with medical problems and has to deal with her personal life.::JV
